title: Travis Fulgham had 10 catches and 150 yards last week. What happens next?
content: The Eagles stumbled onto one of the best WR performances of their last decade. Was it just a flash in the pan, or do they finally have a young talent at the position?

title: The NFL hasn’t ruled out a post-season bubble, but mental health concerns make it unlikely
content: NFL Chief Medical Officer Dr. Allen Sills said the league doesn’t feel adding postseason bubbles is the safest course, factoring in mental concerns.

title: NFL Week 6 Power Rankings: Packers new No. 1 as Chiefs fall, Browns soar into top six
content: Pete Prisco says if the Browns beat Pittsburgh, they can be considered a legit Super Bowl contender

title: The list of PS4 games that don’t work on PS5 just got shorter
content: A few days ago, Sony revealed that 99 percent of PS4 games will be compatible with the PS5 and that there are very few titles you can’t play on the upcoming console.

title: PS4 Firmware Update 8.00 Available to Download Today
content: Pre-set avatars are also getting a bit of a facelift with new pictures to choose from. They include profile pictures from PS4 titles such as Bloodborne, Journey, Ghost of Tsushima, The Last of Us: Part II, and Uncharted 4: A Thief’s End. You can check them all out through here.
